            <div class="content">
              <div class="header">
                <span>Riley H.</span>
                <span>5/16/2017</span>
              </div>
              <div class="description">
                <p lang="en">Really good spot. I like the ambiance and decor as well. <br><br>I ordered a Ham and Cheese Sandwich and had a Strawberry Rhubarb beer. Both were really delicious. Will definitely go back next time in Santa Cruz.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
