              <div class="description">
                <p lang="en">*For Beer Only*<br><br>My goodness, does this place make a decent brew! My boyfriend and I went for beer flights on a Sunday afternoon, and we were not disappointed. My boyfriend ordered the IPA flight. Overall, the selections were interesting,
                  especially the Imp IPA, which was definitely geared towards IPA aficionados. I had the house flight, which was also a great sampling of West End's selection. I particularly enjoyed the American Pale Ale (think craft Blue Moon) and the
                  amber ale. We were there around 12 PM, and while we were seated right away, it definitely picked up by the time we left. Cute, hipster-barn ambiance and friendly staff. Will come back for sure!</p>
              </div>
